---

<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-60"
    style="background: radial-gradient(600px circle at 50% -10%, var(--accent-soft), transparent 60%);"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <div
      class="mx-auto mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-elevated)] px-3 py-1 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]"
    >
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--ok)]"></span>
      infra managed live via Claude + MCP
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text)] sm:text-6xl">
      Akash Chavan
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-[var(--text-muted)] sm:text-xl">
      DevOps / Platform Engineer — infrastructure, CI/CD, and observability, operated
      through an AI SRE workflow.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      This site is the project: a Terraform-provisioned AWS stack, a self-managed
      Kubernetes cluster, GitOps deployments, and real monitoring — all inspectable and
      operable by Claude through nine MCP servers. Scroll down to see how it's built,
      or check the live cluster status below.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="#live-infra"
        class="rounded-md bg-[var(--accent)] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--accent-strong)]"
      >
        View live infra
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="rounded-md border border-[var(--border)] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)] transition-colors hover:border-[var(--accent)]"
      >
        Source on GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:chavanakash2584@gmail.com"
        class="rounded-md border border-[var(--border)] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)] transition-colors hover:border-[var(--accent)]"
      >
        Contact
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
